{"tid":779030,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"白人至上示威不敵反右集會","createTime":"2018-08-14T06:41:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-14T13:24:16.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c18c146ede7a0ba6edae50e3807d97ebc804dfc3","tid":779030,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T06:41:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180814/20475934\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180814%2F20475934&d=ZKH8qiq0938nELvGat%2FllNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=2ce99c40\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180814%2F20475934&h=c95fc203\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180814/20475934</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年08月14日 <br />\n<br />\n白人至上示威不敵反右集會<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180814/large/14wx07p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180814%2Flarge%2F14wx07p.jpg&h=bf725480&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■前日華盛頓有右翼白人示威，在警方和特工護送下企圖突破反歧視者重圍。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國一群白人至上主義示威者，趁去年夏洛茨維爾示威的紀念日，前日在白宮外示威，但人數差強人意。他們更引來一批反對者組織另一場示威，反對他們的政治主張，聲勢更浩大。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n極右集會僅20人出席<br />\n<br />\n去年在夏洛茨維爾的白人至上主義示威，導致1人死亡，其間有大量人士高舉種族主義符號，是美國多年來最大型的同類示威。踏入一周年，他們前日在白宮外舉行了第二次「團結右翼」（Unite the Right）示威，但僅約20人出席，比組織者預計的逾100名參加者為少。<br />\n<br />\n示威組織者凱斯勒認為參加人數偏少的原因是交通問題，但有參加者則向有線新聞網絡（CNN）記者指，支持者都被去年發生的事件嚇怕。<br />\n<br />\n另一邊廂，反對者則在相同地點舉辦示威，人數有數千之眾。當地警方需築起人牆，並架設鐵馬將兩路人馬分隔。而白人至上主義者抵達白宮外不久後隨即離開，雙方未有發生衝突。<br />\n<br />\n白人至上主義者在美國自2016年起重回公眾眼前，不少媒體將此現象與美國總統特朗普當年的競選策略及言論扣連。在去年示威發生後，特朗普只在數日後不點名譴責參與各方，包括反對者在內的暴力，引來輿論批評。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n前幕僚公開被炒絕密錄音　白宮斥無誠信<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n西班牙慶典塌台316人傷"},{"pid":"05b512710cb488262a8f15086d90d4093e006273","tid":779030,"uid":52215,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T06:49:12.000Z","msg":"child登仔仲唔去加入白人至上組織<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有免費洋腸食喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1067644265f5eeedf7fb4afebe109be2e93ac37c","tid":779030,"uid":57677,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T08:01:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e1366fd1cd439d3d002cdbd2401db8e5cd81627","tid":779030,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T08:01:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>child登仔仲唔去加入白人至上組織<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\r有免費洋腸食喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\r<br />\r<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a08a9d4f931d362d318bcbb60cee432d8a23dedc","tid":779030,"uid":113626,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T08:02:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無白人管治香港你地今日仲做緊鄰國奴隸"},{"pid":"ad6c40652d1a7f21119a0a46d213f43d6bb42e8c","tid":779030,"uid":110019,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T08:06:46.000Z","msg":"左膠唔係好大愛包容架咩，連人地示威集會都唔畀<br />\n伊斯蘭咁右左膠反而就包容大愛"},{"pid":"76cc588d7054e7e25103dfad79cedcb606d39806","tid":779030,"uid":129739,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T08:09:42.000Z","msg":"連登仔應該去美國支持白人至上集會，咁到時就唔止20個，而係成千上萬個示威者，撐起半個美國天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7d33f0787a9485d8e11ae9859e23ce1d3cbfe10","tid":779030,"uid":170229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T13:24:16.000Z","msg":"反映咗大把被極左標誌嘅人根本係中左/中右，而唔係極右 white supremacists"}]}